---
title: Turkey Meatballs and Savoury Thyme Gravy with Roasted Potatoes and Sugar Snap Peas
description: Meatballs, potatoes and gravy – a classic combo! Need we say more? The easy thyme-onion gravy makes tonight's plate rich and flavourful. This dish is timeless and perfect for all nights of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-dinde-et-sauce-au-thym-savoureuse-c69f3c50.jpg
